io.github.utk003.util.data.immutable

Class ImmutableNTuple<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.utk003.util.data.immutable.ImmutableNTuple<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The general type of the objects in the N-tuple

    public final class ImmutableNTuple<T>
extends Object
    An immutable N-tuple of objects of type T.

    The ImmutableNTuple<T> class is primarily designed for use in parameterized applications such as in Lists, Sets, and Maps. This class provides an immutable N-tuple of the given objects.

    This class can be paired with Ref<K> if mutable N-tuples are desired, or MutableNTuple can be used instead.
